Name: Student Loan Relational
RelevantInfo: The predicate no_payment_due/1 is true for those people who are not required to repay a student loan.  Auxiliary relations can be used to fully discriminate positive from negative instances of no_payment_due/1.  Closed world assumption applies to all auxiliary relations.
